00:00:16.477 --> 00:00:18.477
Today we are making instant carrot pickle.

00:00:32.710 --> 00:00:34.710
We are making fresh carrot pickle with less oil.

00:00:51.002 --> 00:00:53.002
Put thinly sliced carrots in a bowl.

00:00:52.848 --> 00:00:54.848
Add nigella seeds.

00:00:58.045 --> 00:01:00.045
Add fenugreek seeds.

00:01:02.276 --> 00:01:04.276
Add split mustard seeds.

00:01:07.099 --> 00:01:09.099
Add asafoetida.

00:01:10.575 --> 00:01:12.575
Add chilli powder.

00:01:15.000 --> 00:01:17.000
Add turmeric powder.

00:01:20.814 --> 00:01:22.814
Add salt to taste.

00:01:31.493 --> 00:01:33.493
Mix well.

00:01:36.827 --> 00:01:38.827
Heat the mustard oil.

00:01:43.792 --> 00:01:45.790
This pickle lasts 3 days.

00:01:53.000 --> 00:01:55.000
Store in the fridge and serve with rotis.

00:02:07.493 --> 00:02:09.490
Add hot oil  to the carrot mixture.

00:02:11.843 --> 00:02:13.840
Mix well.

